## SEMrush Tagging Groups

When importing keywords, tag by:
- `restaurants` — all food/dining terms
- `hotels` — all accommodation terms
- `bars-nightlife` — bars, pubs, live music
- `attractions` — pier, beaches, formby, marine lake
- `events` — airshow, flower show, fireworks, festivals
- `the-open-2026` — all Open Championship terms
- `mlec` — all MLEC/Light Fantastic terms
- `shopping` — lord street, shops
- `brand` — branded southportguide terms
